  ],
  "remarks": "Fund for the Development of Weapons Technologies and Production “Lobaev Foundation” (Lobaev Foundation) is a unit of the Lobaev Group of entities and collects funds to finance the projects of LLC Trading House Lobaev Arms. Lobaev Arms rifles are used by the Russian Armed Forces in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. Popular use has made Lobaev Arms rifles one of the symbols of Russia’s war of aggression. Lobaev Foundation is financing new developments in the weapons sector and production of unmanned aerial vehicles, is shipping weapons and ammunition to the special services and military units, and is fundraising money to finance those activities. The Lobaev Foundation provides assistance to the servicemen of the Ministry of Defence of the Russian Federation and the Federal Security Service of the Russian Federation. The Lobaev Foundation therefore supports actions which undermine and threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine, and supports and benefits from the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}